0 0 12 9 rectfill
q
0 0 12 9 re W n
% Fallback Image: x=0 y=0 w=12 h=9 res=300ppi size=5700
[ 12 0 0 -9.12 0 9.12 ] concat
/cairo_ascii85_file currentfile /ASCII85Decode filter def
/DeviceRGB setcolorspace
